Comment: 0,0:05:56.47,0:05:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-----------------text-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,飯能阿爾卑斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.06,0:01:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,據說是從天覽山一直延伸至秩父那塊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而因此得名的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那我明天的休息日就去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我明天和家人開車去兜風來著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是喔 那就沒辦法囉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.03,0:01:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,妳一個人沒問題麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.03,0:01:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,本來就離得蠻近的 別擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:02:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,天覽山和前面的多峰主山都有去過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這次就爬天覺山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.63,0:02:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在東吾野站下車
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,從天覺山一路往大高山走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.97,0:02:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,還能順便適應新的登山靴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,路上注意安全喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,帶上這些飯糰去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好重！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好大！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,也做了日向的份喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然今天只有我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.41,0:02:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不過如果跟媽媽照實說會讓她擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我出發啦{\fn FOT-Seurat ProN DB}♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然很重不過正好能鍛鍊體力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.45,0:02:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我得為了明年重新挑戰富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,而努力積累經驗和鍛鍊體力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,飯能阿爾卑斯會是怎樣的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好令人期待喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:03:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正楷体_GBK\c&H00E97D50\3c&H00FFFFFF\i1\b1\fs60\bord4\pos(640,396.429)}『飯能的阿爾卑斯！？』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,抵達東吾野站！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好沉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不過這也是訓練的一環
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,天覺山是往這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,湯手是什麼呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.97,0:03:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,走咧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好涼快{\fn FOT-Seurat ProN DB}♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,澤筋路線和尾根路線？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,尾根是以虛線標記的也就是難度高的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就走澤筋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好安靜喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,因為都沒人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在可是獨自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不僅是走的路線
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,連其它一切都由我自己做主！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,時而快{\fn FOT-Seurat ProN DB}♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,時而慢{\fn FOT-Seurat ProN DB}♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可以完全照著自己的節奏來走{\fn FOT-Seurat ProN DB}♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,愛怎麼就怎麼樣{\c&H7A7BFF&}❤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這座山的一切一切都是哀家的{\fn FOT-Seurat ProN DB}♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,繁星墜落的山坳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,登山靴呀滑下雪坡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,心上人啊你會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:05:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,銜著花朵迎接我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,觸動了…我的心窩…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,思念你這…登山者啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,讀不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,走這裡沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,遇不到人也沒法確認
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我跨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,還好帶了手套
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.33,0:05:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧了新靴子腳還沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就是背包太沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好辛苦 一點都不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,要不回家算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我想見到你{\fn FOT-Seurat ProN DB}♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,溫柔和藹的你{\fn FOT-Seurat ProN DB}♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:07:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好想快一點見到你{\fn FOT-Seurat ProN DB}♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:06:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,幻聽？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you 髭羚先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,幻覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 葵姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,心奈醬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,妳沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,沒…沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,只是稍微休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為妳半路暈厥了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不過還真巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我是特地來見髭羚先生的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,心奈醬是走哪兒上來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我走的是澤筋路線
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我是由尾根路線走來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,跟坐在夢馬君身上似的{\fn FOT-Seurat ProN DB}♪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,路上有很棒的夢馬君長椅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,還有很可愛的告示牌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00284C4C\bord0\fn方正喵鸣\fad(0,1000)\fs35\pos(715.2,415.4)}小心有蛇哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,葵姐接下來有什麼打算嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,回家…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我打算走到大高山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我能和葵姐同行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,當然沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,還讓妳幫我背水瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不客氣{\fn FOT-Seurat ProN DB}♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,原來妳在進行挑戰富士山的訓練啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜我被天覺山打敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,把握自己的極限已經是很大的進步了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,只要多加訓練就能跨越障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.89,0:08:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,心奈醬說的話就是靠譜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,葵姐 妳那雙是新的登山靴嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 一咬牙就買下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,心奈醬的鞋子是生日時母親送的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是的{\fn FOT-Seurat ProN DB}♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,心奈醬 心奈醬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,髭羚先生的親子一家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.23,0:09:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然獨自一人很自由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但還是與人相伴最開心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這是爆彈飯糰呢{\fn FOT-Seurat ProN DB}♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝葵姐{\c&H7A7BFF&}❤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.95,0:09:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己也吃不完兩塊那麼大的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,梅子！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,剛好能刺激疲憊的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,真的 好好吃{\fn FOT-Seurat ProN DB}♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,代我向葵媽媽說聲謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然原本只打算爬到這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,心奈醬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,要不我們再多走走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,要的要的{\fn FOT-Seurat ProN DB}♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:10:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 前面還有個好去處
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好去處？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好宏偉的杉樹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.23,0:10:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,葵姐走這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好鮮艷的仁王像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,子之權現天龍寺？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,對 就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這是啥 草鞋麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,子之權現祭祀著守護腰與腿的神佛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,「魔火時有侵蝕腰足 煎熬世人」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,「因此若為腰足痛楚所擾」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,「誠心祈願 神佛自有靈驗」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,意思就是只要在這裡祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,神就能保佑妳的腿腳不受傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我想正好葵姐在進行訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.64,0:10:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就想說帶妳來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,祈禱希望葵姐明年平安登上富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我誠心拜託您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,保佑我這次能登上富士山最頂端
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正喵鸣\frz270\3c&H00284C4C\t(1,2958,\fs55)\\move(1144.8,481.343,1199.657,503.057)}東京天空塔眺望處
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,真舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,也很累人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可是一旦抵達終點就都值得了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,心奈醬 謝謝妳陪著我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我過得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不會 我也過得很開心{\fn FOT-Seurat ProN DB}♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,飯能阿爾卑斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,還蠻棘手的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不過一路走過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,還算是攢了不少自信…吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,待續{\fn FOT-Seurat ProN DB}♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來湯手到底是啥
Comment: 0,0:05:56.47,0:05:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-----------------ed-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:27.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}夢に向かい　ダーツなげたら　いい音　ふたつ鳴ったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:32.49,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}無茶な　足音　鳴らし　駆けだそう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:38.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}図書室でしか見たことない　世界　確かめたい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:43.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}ナビは　太陽と　繋いだ手だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:47.04,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}「春はヒバリと作戦会議」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:49.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}「夏はバッタと一点突破」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:55.40,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}なんで地球が丸いか知ってる？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:58.09,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}「秋は赤トンボと骨休め」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.49,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}「冬はハリモグラと夢の中」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:05.72,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}この場所に帰ってくるため
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:08.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}飛行機雲ふわりつかまえて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:11.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}やまびこをガイドにつけて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:16.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}ブランコの助走で　See you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:20.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}繋いだ手と手を　離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.77,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}おそろいの夢　消さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:28.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}片っぽずつ　翼　寄せあって　飛ぼう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:27.28,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}朝著夢想丟出飛鏢　傳來兩聲清脆迴響
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:32.49,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}發出倔強的腳步聲　不懈地向前奔跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:38.31,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}好想走出圖書室　看一看書裡寫的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:43.11,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}唯有太陽和與你牽在一起的手為我導航
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:47.04,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}「春天和雲雀一起召開會議」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:49.47,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}「夏天和飛蝗一起勇往直前」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:55.40,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}知道地球為什麼是圓形的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:58.09,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}「秋天和赤蜻一起暫作小憩」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.49,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}「冬天和針鼴一起沉眠夢境」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:05.72,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}是為了讓我們最終回到原地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:08.98,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}伸手抓住輕飄飄的飛機雲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:11.67,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}請山中的精靈將我們指引
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:16.88,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}在鞦韆的助力下　與你相約在明天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:20.03,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}不要將牽在一起的手鬆開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.77,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}不要讓你我共同的夢消散
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:28.47,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\bord4}將異色的孤翼湊到一起　結伴飛翔
